==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dynamist
<hw>Dy"na*mist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who accounts
for material phenomena by a theory of dynamics.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Those who would resolve matter into centers of force may be said
to constitute the school of <qex>dynamists</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Ward
(Dyn. Sociol. ).</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dynamitard</ent>⟦br⟧
